# AI Blog Generation Feature

Add an AI-powered blog creation system to the DiskDoctor admin panel with two modes: **Guided** (user provides topic/notes) and **MagicAI** (fully automatic — analyzes existing content, finds trending gaps, generates everything).

---

## User Review Required

> [!IMPORTANT]
> **LLM Provider**: The plan defaults to **OpenAI** (`gpt-4o` for text, gpt images for images).

> [!IMPORTANT]
> **API Key Storage**: The API key will be stored **plaintext in MongoDB** (same as your existing admin credentials pattern). If you want encryption at rest, let me know.

> [!IMPORTANT]
> **Image Generation**: The plan uses gpt to generate featured images. This costs ~$0.04-0.08 per image. If you'd rather skip AI image generation and just leave featured image empty for manual upload, let me know.

> [!WARNING]
> **Web Search for MagicAI**: For the "search what's hot right now" part, I have two options:
> 1. **Option A** — Use OpenAI's `gpt-4o` with a smart prompt that leverages its training knowledge to suggest trending topics in the data recovery niche (no external API needed, simpler)
> 2. **Option B** — Integrate a gpt web search API 
>
> **My recommendation**: Start with **Option A** (LLM-only) — the model can reason well about content gaps and suggest strong topics without real-time search. We can always add search later. Let me know your preference.

---

## Architecture Overview

```mermaid
graph TB
    subgraph Dashboard["Admin Dashboard"]
        A["⚙️ AI Settings<br/>(API Key, Model)"]
        B["🪄 MagicAI Button"]
        C["✍️ Guided Generate"]
    end

    subgraph API["New API Routes"]
        D["POST /api/admin/ai-settings<br/>Save API Key"]
        E["GET /api/admin/ai-settings<br/>Get Settings"]
        F["POST /api/blogs/ai-generate<br/>Generate Blog"]
    end

    subgraph LLM["OpenAI"]
        G["GPT-4o<br/>Text Generation"]
        H["DALL-E 3<br/>Image Generation"]
    end

    subgraph Existing["Existing Infrastructure"]
        I["MongoDB<br/>blogDB.settings<br/>blogDB.blogs"]
        J["Cloudinary<br/>AI-generated images"]
        K["POST /api/blogs<br/>Save final blog"]
    end

    A -->|"Store key"| D
    D --> I
    B -->|"mode: magic"| F
    C -->|"mode: guided + topic"| F
    F -->|"Fetch existing blogs"| I
    F -->|"Generate text"| G
    F -->|"Generate image"| H
    H -->|"Upload to CDN"| J
    F -->|"Return generated data"| Dashboard
    Dashboard -->|"Admin edits & publishes"| K
```

