### Admin UI — Settings Modal

#### [MODIFY] [page.tsx](file:///Users/abdulmajeed/Downloads/DiskDoctor/src/app/admin/dashboard/page.tsx)

Add to the dashboard:

1. **Settings gear icon** in the header bar (next to "+ New Post" and "Logout")
2. **AI Settings Modal** — opens on click with:
   - API Key input (password-masked with show/hide toggle)
   - Model dropdown: `gpt-4o` (recommended), `gpt-4o-mini` (cheaper)
   - Image Model dropdown: `dall-e-3` (recommended), `dall-e-2` (cheaper)
   - "Test Connection" button — validates the key
   - "Save" button
   - Status indicator (✅ Connected / ❌ Not configured)

3. **MagicAI Button** — a prominent sparkle/wand button next to "+ New Post":
   - Disabled if no API key is configured
   - On click → shows a modal with two tabs:
     - **🪄 MagicAI** — one-click, shows a progress stepper: "Analyzing existing content → Finding trending topic → Generating blog → Creating image → Done!"
     - **✍️ Guided** — shows a form with: Topic (required), Additional Notes (optional), Target Word Count (slider: 800–2500, default 1200)
   - Both modes call `POST /api/blogs/ai-generate`
   - When complete → redirects to `/admin/editor?ai=true&data=<encoded>` with the generated content pre-filled in the editor for review/editing before publishing

