### Admin UI — Editor Integration

#### [MODIFY] [page.tsx](file:///Users/abdulmajeed/Downloads/DiskDoctor/src/app/admin/editor/page.tsx)

Add support for receiving AI-generated content:

1. On mount, check for `?ai=true` query param
2. If present, read the AI-generated data from `sessionStorage` (set by the dashboard before redirect)
3. Pre-fill all editor fields: title, content, excerpt, meta description, focus keyword, slug, category, tags, featured image
4. Show a dismissible blue banner at the top: "✨ AI-Generated — Review and edit before publishing"

